### 1. Create Model Type (Global - without clientId)
POST {{API_URL}}/api/model-types
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "name": "Tipo de Modelo Global",
  "description": "Este es un tipo de modelo global disponible para todos los clientes"
}


### 2. Create Model Type (Specific - with clientId)
POST {{API_URL}}/api/model-types
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "name": "Tipo de Modelo Específico",
  "description": "Este es un tipo de modelo específico para un cliente",
  "clientId": "{{CLIENT_ID}}"
}


### 3. Get All Model Types (without pagination)
GET {{API_URL}}/api/model-types
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


### 4. Get All Model Types (with pagination)
GET {{API_URL}}/api/model-types?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


### 5. Get Model Types filtered by Client ID
GET {{API_URL}}/api/model-types?clientId={{CLIENT_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


### 6. Get Model Types filtered by Client ID (with pagination)
GET {{API_URL}}/api/model-types?page=1&limit=10&clientId={{CLIENT_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}


